name: Bireleys Mango Drink
description: Bireley's is a brand of non-carbonated, fruit-flavored soft drinks currently owned by Asahi in Japan.

name: Fanta Grape
description: Fanta Grape is a mellow grape flavored carbonated drink containing vitamin B6.

name: Q00 Apple Drink
description: The fruit juice brand "Qoo" was released in 1999, and its name comes from the sound of satisfaction a grown-up makes when they down a glass of beer. In September 2012 Qoo became part of the Minute Maid brand.

name: Gabunomi Melon Cream Soda
description: This outstanding limited edition soda release by Pokka Sapporo gives you an accurate melon cream soda flavor. It is cloudy green in color since it contains condensed milk, which gives it creamy taste.

name: Pokka Lemon Tea
description: Pokka Ice Lemon Tea is a refreshing blend of 100% real brewed premium black tea infused with real lemon juice.

name: Georgia Ice Cocoa
description: Made with 100% dutch cocoa and 100% hokkaido cream. Scored low due to a watery taste.

name: Asahi Dodekamin Energy Soda
description: Dodekamin is a popular energy soda in Japan, similar to Lifeguard and Dekavita C

name: Fanta Okinawa Shikuwasa
description: This Fanta flavor is fueled by the Shikuwasa fruit, which is a green, tangy, lemon-like citrus fruit grown in the southern Japanese tropical island of Okinawa. This exotic soda flavor truly speaks for all things tropical!

name: Papico Ice Cream
description: Produced by Glico, Papico comes in the shape of two mini bottles that you have to pull apart. You then detach the top part of each of the bottle-shaped plastic and you slurp. As it thaws, it gradually becomes a shake. Flavors usually come in chocolate coffee, white sour and grape, but there usually many more seasonal, limited-time, flavors throughout the year
